message.body: Wanna pick up stuff in am? Just let me know when and I'll pack a bag for ya!
Hey, it would be easier if I could stop by this evening (collecting a pup at star in the am), would that work for you?
Sweet! I'll make up some bags! Can you fit a folding table in your car? ;)
I actually have a table that I need to take to an art thing post-race, so I think all I'll need is the banner & propaganda! I can come by in an hour or so if that works? Thank you!
For the first time in my life I'm running early. Be there in 5-10?
Everything went well this morning! I can drop the stuff back off any time after 1230 or so? ￼
Sweet!! I should be home by 12:30!!
Might be closer to 1? No rush either. ;)
Be there in half an hour? Thanks!
